column2: select B.BA_NO, B.MOBILE_NO, B.BILLING_SYSTEM, C.COMPANY_ABBR, B.EXCESS_BAL_ID, B.STATUS, B.CN_ID, B.RECEIPT_ID, B.TOPUP_ID from PMDB..PM_BATCH_CONVERT_POST_PRE B inner join PMDB..PM_PREPAID_LOAD_BATCH LD on (B.BATCH_ID = LD.BATCH_ID) inner join PMDB..PM_COMPANY C on (B.COMPANY_ID = C.COMPANY_ID) where LD.ORDER_ID = @order_id
